.DT
add_mailer
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_mailer

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_mailer -  This method adds in a mailer for a specific player into the current list of mailers.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_mailer(object ob,
string str)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the mailer for the player
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - the player the mailer is for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
return 1 if successful

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/mail_track.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds in a mailer for a specific player into the current
list of mailers.
.EP

